{"tid":1135452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地翁首次搭飛機　嫌落機排隊人多開緊急逃生門","createTime":"2019-05-02T10:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T10:18:15.000Z","uid":241764,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fd9b956af9280ec61a85adfc67f8d0deeb8f6e62","tid":1135452,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T10:13:52.000Z","msg":"內地一名首次乘搭飛的老伯，下飛機時見輪候的人太多，不想排隊，見旁邊有門就直接打開而誤開緊急逃生門。他見到開門後沒有樓梯才返回機艙，機組人員手忙腳亂緊急修復和關門，未致影響後續航班，老伯終被公安行政拘留10日。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的山東航空SC8823航班，日前從濟南飛抵浙江舟山普陀山機場，乘客排隊落機時，一名65歲宋姓男乘客突然打開緊急逃生門想直接離開。普陀山機場公案分局向他詢問時，他表示這是第一次搭飛機，下飛機時嫌排隊人太多，就想從「邊門」離開。開門後老伯才發現沒梯子，只好放棄捷徑回到機艙內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20190502/s00004/1556780515729/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%BF%81%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E6%90%AD%E9%A3%9B%E6%A9%9F-%E5%AB%8C%E8%90%BD%E6%A9%9F%E6%8E%92%E9%9A%8A%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%9A%E9%96%8B%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E9%80%83%E7%94%9F%E9%96%80%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190502%2Fs00004%2F1556780515729%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25BF%2581%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%2590%25AD%25E9%25A3%259B%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E5%25AB%258C%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%2596%2580%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E3%2580%2591&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=2e942b7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190502%2Fs00004%2F1556780515729%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25BF%2581%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%2590%25AD%25E9%25A3%259B%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E5%25AB%258C%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%